<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= name %> - Privacy Policy</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #374151;
            max-width: 720px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 48px 24px;
            background: #fff;
        }
        h1 { font-size: 1.875em; font-weight: 700; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.25em; }
        h2 { font-size: 1.25em; font-weight: 600; color: #1f2937; margin-top: 2.5em; margin-bottom: 0.75em; }
        p { margin-bottom: 1em; }
        ul { padding-left: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1em; }
        li { margin-bottom: 0.5em; }
        a { color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none; }
        a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        .meta { color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.875em; margin-bottom: 2.5em; }
        .app-name { font-weight: 600; color: #111827; }
        footer { margin-top: 4em; padding-top: 2em; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-size: 0.875em; color: #6b7280; }
        footer a { color: #6b7280; margin-right: 1.5em; }
        footer a:hover { color: #2563eb; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p class="meta">Last Updated: <%= updated_date %></p>

<p>This Privacy Policy explains how <span class="app-name"><%= name %></span> ("we", "our", or "the App") handles your information. By using the App, you agree to the practices described below.</p>

<h2>What We Collect</h2>
<p>We collect minimal information necessary to provide and improve our services:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Usage Data</strong> - Anonymous statistics about how you interact with the App, including features used and session duration.</li>
    <li><strong>Device Information</strong> - Basic technical data such as device type, operating system version, and app version for compatibility purposes.</li>
    <li><strong>Crash Reports</strong> - When errors occur, we may collect diagnostic information to help us identify and fix issues.</li>
</ul>
<p>We do not collect personal information such as your name, email address, or location unless you voluntarily provide it.</p>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>The information we collect is used to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Operate and maintain the App</li>
    <li>Analyze usage patterns to improve user experience</li>
    <li>Diagnose technical problems and fix bugs</li>
    <li>Develop new features based on user behavior</li>
</ul>

<% if (third_party_services && third_party_services.length > 0) { %>
<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>The App integrates with the following third-party services that may collect and process data according to their own privacy policies:</p>
<ul>
    <% third_party_services.forEach(service => { %>
    <li>
        <% if (service.url) { %>
        <a href="<%= service.url %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><%= service.name %></a>
        <% } else { %>
        <%= service.name %>
        <% } %>
    </li>
    <% }); %>
</ul>
<p>We encourage you to review their privacy policies to understand how they handle your data.</p>
<% } %>

<h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>
<p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. However, no method of electronic transmission or storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
<p>Data may be processed and stored on servers located in different regions. By using the App, you consent to this transfer of information.</p>

<h2>Your Choices</h2>
<p>You have control over your data:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Opt-out of Analytics</strong> - You may disable analytics collection through your device settings or within the App if such option is available.</li>
    <li><strong>Data Deletion</strong> - Contact us to request deletion of any data associated with your use of the App.</li>
    <li><strong>Access</strong> - You may request information about what data we have collected about you.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>The App is not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we become aware that we have collected such information, we will take steps to delete it promptly.</p>

<h2>Policy Updates</h2>
<p>We may revise this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we make changes, we will update the "Last Updated" date at the top of this page. Continued use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>For questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or your personal data, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:<%= email %>"><%= email %></a></p>

<footer>
    <a href="../home/">Home</a>
    <a href="../privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>
    <a href="../terms/">Terms of Service</a>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
